&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;The TCT controller for color change repeats Pin opening/closing at a high speed, realizing an increased flow rate due to condensed pressure and eliminating dead spots in gate and tip sections at a high speed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

